'''3rd age equipment''' are a group of [[members]] items obtained by completing the highest tiers of [[Treasure Trails]] (hard and above). There are four combat sets, plus an [[3rd age axe|axe]], a [[3rd age pickaxe|pickaxe]], a [[Ring of 3rd age|ring]] and a [[3rd age cloak|cloak]].

Lore-wise, they resemble what people used to wear for combat during the 3rd age of [[Gielinor]].

